#

Risotto alla Milanese

40 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodEasy

Description

A creamy, luxurious saffron-infused rice dish that's simple to prepare yet impressively indulgent.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • chicken broth: 4 cups
  • saffron threads: 1 pinch
  • onion: 1, finely chopped
  • dry white wine: 1/2 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
